        <h1>Cabbage Stir Fry</h1>
       <div class="recipe-details">
         <img src="cabbage-stir-fry.jpeg" alt="Cabbage Stir Fry" class="recipe-image">
       
            <div class="ingredients">
                <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>1 small cabbage, shredded</li>
                    <li>1 onion, sliced</li>
                    <li>1 tsp mustard seeds</li>
                    <li>1/2 tsp turmeric powder</li>
                    <li>2 green chilies, slit</li>
                    <li>Salt to taste</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="instructions">
                <h2>Instructions:</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Heat oil in a pan, add mustard seeds, and let them splutter.</li>
                    <li>Add sliced onion and green chilies, saute until soft.</li>
                    <li>Add turmeric and shredded cabbage, and stir-fry for 5 minutes.</li>
                    <li>Season with salt and cook for another 5 minutes until cabbage is tender.</li>
                    <li>Serve hot with rice or flatbread.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
